Hero.title: <important>Pride Logistics (P) Ltd. : </important> Women-Led Solutions for Nepal's Supply Chain needs.
Hero.description: Pride Logistics is a leading logistics company in Nepal, specializing in efficient, reliable, and cost-effective supply chain solutions. We offer a wide range of services including freight forwarding, warehousing, distribution, and last-mile delivery across Nepal and beyond. With a focus on timely deliveries, modern tracking systems, and exceptional customer service, Pride Logistics ensures seamless movement of goods for businesses of all sizes.

Features.section_title: Unlock the Full Potential of the Pride Logistics (P) Ltd.
Features.section_description: A free and open-source landing page template for your SaaS business, built with React, TypeScript, Shadcn UI, and Tailwind CSS.
Features.feature1_description: We handle your both import and export cargos finding what you need on real time with competitive offer and consistent service for your shipment. We provide complete logistic services and solution from door to door, port to port and airport to airport at personalized level.
Features.feature2_description: We also provide consolidation services for your shipment. Whether the volume/quantity of your shipment is small that does not maintain the full container, we combine it with our other regular shipments destined to same destination. This service will be a cost effective and delivered safely within the given time frame.
Features.feature3_description: When required, we make your job easy by picking up the shipment at your factory/ warehouse and delivering it to client’s final door stop. This service includes all shipping, handling, and import and custom duties.
Features.feature4_description: Depending upon the situation and requirement, combined transport facility is catered with a thorough control over all the steps involved in international transport, including multiple storages and handling stages.
Features.feature5_description: We also meet our customer’s need for receiving, storage and distribution processing of goods within a professional standard and depending upon different shapes, sizes and nature of goods.
Features.feature6_description: No doubt, there involve risks in any businesses and pace we take. It would be better to stay at safe side to avoid heavy losses which are definitely unpredictable. Therefore, we secure our clients by providing marine insurance for their shipments depending upon the requirements.
Features.feature7_description: We handle different types of goods to various parts of the globe. We arrange the shipments accordingly to the nature of the cargo following proper standards and allowing goods to reach its destination without any hassle.
